_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The teams will face each other once in their group, a total of three games, from July 27 to August 4.\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1975, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The top two teams from each group advance to the first-round quarterfinal knockout stage as will the two best third-placed teams, determined by wins, point differential, and other relative measurements of group play competitiveness.\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 2208, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The quarterfinals will be played on Tuesday, August 6.\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2264, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The semifinals will be played on Thursday, August 8 and the medal games will be played on Saturday, August 10.\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2375, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There will be a draw following the conclusion of group play to determine the knockout matchups.\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2472, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Teams who qualify will be placed in four pots.\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2519, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pot D will have the two best group winners.\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2563, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pot E will have the worst group winner and highest ranking second-place team.\", \"from\": 2564, \"to\": 2641, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pot F will have the other two second-placed teams, and Pot G will have the two third-placed group play teams who qualified.\", \"from\": 2642, \"to\": 2765, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Teams from the same group cannot face each other again in the quarterfinals.\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2843, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The two teams from Pot D (the two best group winners) are not permitted to face each other again until the medal games.\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2963, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Losing quarterfinal teams will not participate in any further games.\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 3032, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Positions 5-8 will be determined based on performance in games played.\", \"from\": 3033, \"to\": 3103, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00c2\\u00a9 2026Minute Media-All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 3105, \"to\": 3145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The content on this site is for entertainment and educational purposes only.\", \"from\": 3146, \"to\": 3222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Betting and gambling content is intended for individuals 21+ and is based on individual commentators' opinions and not that of Minute Media or its affiliates and related brands.\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3400, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All picks and predictions are suggestions only and not a guarantee of success or profit.\", \"from\": 3401, \"to\": 3489, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you or someone you know has a gambling problem, crisis counseling and referral services can be accessed by calling 1-800-GAMBLER.\", \"from\": 3490, \"to\": 3622, \"entities\": []}]}"